dat1 <- read.csv("~/Dropbox/Shared/Mobility_Analysis/Data/gorgas_gps_v3.csv", 
                 stringsAsFactors = F) %>%
#dat1 <- read.csv("~/GORGAS/gorgas_gps_v3.csv") %>%
  mutate(inf=ifelse(infected==1,"infected","no infected")) %>%
  filter(Longitud<(-72.8)) %>%
  filter(!(ID==744 & Latitud<(-3.46))) %>%
  filter(!(ID==714 & Longitud>(-73.31))) %>%
  filter(!(ID==715 & Longitud<(-73.328))) %>%
  filter(ID %in% c(703,705,706,708,710,713,717,718,719,724,726,727,728,731,733,745,747,748,749,750)) %>% # Final selection of participants see SFIG1
  group_by(ID) %>% mutate(disp=(max(Longitud)-min(Longitud))+(max(Latitud)-min(Latitud)),
                          disp_cat=cut(disp, breaks=c(-Inf, 0.05, 0.3, Inf), labels=F)) %>%
  ungroup() %>% # Same routine as SFIG1
  group_by(ID, date) %>%
  mutate(n=n(),#date1=ymd_hms(POSIXt), date2=as.POSIXct(POSIXt), 
         date1 = mdy_hm(POSIXt),
         diff_h=as.numeric(max(date1)-min(date1), units = "hours")) %>%
  ungroup() %>%
  group_by(ID) %>%
  mutate(days=n()) %>%
  filter(diff_h>12) %>%
  mutate(days2=n()) %>%
  filter(days2>8, n>50) %>%
  ungroup() %>%
  group_by(ID,date) %>%
  mutate(group_id = group_indices())
dat1$disp2<-factor(dat1$disp, labels=unique(dat1$ID)[order(unique(dat1$disp))])

dat1.sf <- sfheaders::sf_point( obj = dat1, x = "Longitud", y = "Latitud", keep = T)
sf::st_crs(dat1.sf) <- 4326

t1 <- dat1 %>% ungroup() %>% group_by(ID) %>%
  summarise(infected = max(infected, na.rm = T),
            infected = ifelse(infected==1, "Ever infected", "Never infected")) %>%
  full_join(read.csv("~/Dropbox/Shared/Mobility_Analysis/Data/master_seguimiento_v10.csv") %>%
              rename(ID = person.id) %>%
              mutate_all(.funs = ~ifelse(.==99,NA,.)) %>%
              group_by(ID) %>%
              summarise(jornalero = max(work.sec.1, na.rm=T),
                        madera = max(work.sec.2, na.rm=T),
                        pesca = max(work.sec.3, na.rm=T),
                        comer = max(work.sec.6, na.rm=T),
                        extract.0 = jornalero + madera + pesca + comer,
                        extract.1 = ifelse(extract.0>0,"out-community","in-community"),
                        infe.0 = max(pcr.mangold.result, na.rm=T),
                        infe.1 = ifelse(infe.0!=0,"Ever infected","Never infected")) %>%
              dplyr::select(ID, extract.1, infe.1),
            by = "ID") %>%
  full_join(read.csv("~/Dropbox/Shared/Mobility_Analysis/Data/Census/individual_v2.csv") %>%
              mutate_all(.funs = ~ifelse(.==99,NA,.)) %>%
              rename(ID = person.id) %>%
              mutate(nm_level_study_cat = cut(nm_level_study, breaks=c(-Inf, 4, 6, Inf), labels=c("Primary or less","Secondary complete or incomplete","Superior"))),
            by = "ID") %>%
  mutate(followup = ifelse(is.na(infected), "No", "Yes")) %>%
  full_join(read.csv("~/Dropbox/Shared/Mobility_Analysis/Data/master_parasitaria_v9.csv") %>%
              mutate_all(.funs = ~ifelse(.==99,NA,.)) %>%
              rename(ID = person.id) %>%
              distinct(ID, .keep_all=T), by = "ID")

bbox_new <- st_bbox(dat1.sf) # current bounding box
xrange <- bbox_new$xmax - bbox_new$xmin # range of x values
yrange <- bbox_new$ymax - bbox_new$ymin # range of y values
bbox_new[1] <- bbox_new[1] - (0.5 * xrange) # xmin - left
bbox_new[3] <- bbox_new[3] + (0.5 * xrange) # xmax - right
bbox_new[2] <- bbox_new[2] - (0.5 * yrange) # ymin - bottom
bbox_new[4] <- bbox_new[4] + (0.5 * yrange) # ymax - top
bbox_new <- bbox_new %>% st_as_sfc()
bbox_new <- as(bbox_new, "Spatial")

# Land Use
area.sf <- st_read("~/Dropbox/Resources/GIS/LugaresPoblados [VISOR LORETO]/LugaresPoblados.shp")
boundary <- st_read("~/Dropbox/Work/GORGAS/Papers/P1_GORGAS_Mob/Analysis/GIS/MAZAN_SHP/MAZAN_SHP.shp") %>%
  st_transform(crs = 32718)

mazan.sf <- area.sf %>%
  st_intersection(boundary) %>%
  st_transform(crs = 4326) %>%
  mutate(CODOBJ = as.numeric(as.character(CODOBJ)),
         NOMOBJ = as.character(NOMOBJ))
##

r <- raster(bbox_new, res = .0001)
gg <- mazan.sf %>% filter(NOMOBJ=="Gamitanacocha") %>%
  st_transform("+proj=longlat +datum=WGS84 +no_defs +ellps=WGS84 +towgs84=0,0,0 ") %>% 
  mutate(long = unlist(map(geometry,1)),
         lat = unlist(map(geometry,2))) %>%
  st_set_geometry(NULL) %>%
  dplyr::select(long,lat)

r_track <- distanceFromPoints(r, gg)
r_track <- projectRaster(r_track, crs="+init=epsg:32718")

dat2 <- dat1.sf %>% ungroup() %>%
  st_transform("+init=epsg:32718") %>%
  group_by(ID) %>% mutate(infected = max(infected)) %>% ungroup() %>%
  mutate(long = unlist(map(geometry,1)),
         lat = unlist(map(geometry,2))) %>%
  st_set_geometry(NULL)

traj <- dat2 %>% ungroup() %>% nest(-ID, -group_id, -infected) %>%
  mutate(traj = map(data, ~TrajFromCoords(., xCol = "long", yCol = "lat", timeCol = "date1", spatialUnits = "m")),
         Ncoords = map(traj, ~TrajGetNCoords(.)),
         StepLengths = map(traj, ~mean(TrajStepLengths(.))),
         Length = map(traj, ~TrajLength(.)),
         Duration = map(traj, ~TrajDuration(.)),
         #MeanVelocity = map(traj, ~TrajMeanVelocity(.)),
         #Derivatives = map(traj, ~TrajDerivatives(.)),
         ExpectedSquareDisplacement = map(traj, ~TrajExpectedSquareDisplacement(.)),
         trk = lapply(data, function(d) { mk_track(d, long, lat, .t = date1, crs = sp::CRS("+init=epsg:32718"))}),
         steps = lapply(trk, function(x) { x %>% extract_covariates(r_track)}),
         summ = lapply(steps, function(x) { x %>%
             mutate(index = ifelse(layer == max(x$layer), 1, 0), index = ifelse(layer == min(x$layer), 1, index)) %>%
             filter(index==1) %>%
             mutate(t_h = as.numeric(max(t_)-min(t_), units = "hours"), d_km = (max(layer)-min(layer))/1000) %>%
             dplyr::select(t_h,d_km) %>%
             slice(1)
         }))

ll <- traj %>% dplyr::select(ID, group_id, infected, Ncoords, StepLengths, Length, Duration, ExpectedSquareDisplacement, summ) %>% 
  unnest() %>%
  mutate(StepLengths = StepLengths/1000,
         Length = Length/1000,
         Duration = Duration/60/60,
         ExpectedSquareDisplacement = ExpectedSquareDisplacement/1000000,
         count=1)
ll_summ <- ll %>% dplyr::select(-ID, -group_id) %>%
  group_by(infected) %>%
  summarise_all(.funs = list(sum, mean, sd), na.rm=T)

ll_summ

dat_all <- dat1 %>% ungroup() %>% 
  group_by(ID) %>% mutate(infected = max(infected)) %>% ungroup() %>%
  nest(-ID, -infected)

dat_all <- dat_all %>%
  mutate(trk = lapply(data, function(d) {
    mk_track(d, Longitud, Latitud, .t = date1, crs = sp::CRS("+init=epsg:4326"))
  }))

# Sample rate
dat_all %>% mutate(sr = lapply(trk, summarize_sampling_rate)) %>%
  select(ID, infected, sr) %>% unnest()

# iSSF
m1 <- dat_all %>% mutate(steps = lapply(trk, function(x) {
  x %>% track_resample(rate = minutes(10), tolerance = minutes(2)) %>%
    filter_min_n_burst(min_n = 3) %>%
    steps_by_burst() %>% random_steps(n_control=10) %>% 
    extract_covariates(r_gg) %>%
    mutate(village = ifelse(is.na(village),999, village),
           village_end = factor(village #, ordered = T
                                ))
}))

m2 <- m1 %>% dplyr::select(ID, infected, steps) %>% unnest(cols = c(steps)) %>%

  )
